article_title: If TennCare is expanded, it may initially focus only on mentally ill

article_metadata.description: A Republican-dominated task force examining ways to expand health care in Tennessee might be favoring a phased-in approach that would initially cover only a small percentage of the state's uninsured, but might then be expanded assuming the program meets its goals.
